{"id": 967, "genre": 1001, "title": "抛开现实，你理想中的职业是什么？", "description": "如果可以让你放下手头的一切，你最想做的一份工作是什么？（题图来自：HELENA PEREZ GARCIA）", "record_count": 5306, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130120WLl7nFsMN4Z8VGQY.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-05-09T11:22:14Z", "options": [{"id": 75520, "content": "旅行家", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 498183}, {"id": 75776, "content": "可以全世界飞的导游吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 575744}, {"id": 76032, "content": "默默的看着你们", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166753}, {"id": 76288, "content": "找个安静的山村。带上雕刻刀。做木雕。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 567750}, {"id": 76544, "content": "NBA球星", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599999}, {"id": 76800, "content": "孤独的美食旅行家", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193026AFZbJHjxKeE1VmYf.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603384}, {"id": 75521, "content": "收藏家", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296767}, {"id": 75777, "content": "自由撰稿人。旅行 拍照 吃美食 写东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597183}, {"id": 76033, "content": "画手，写手，搞艺术，翻译官～应该顺便问下现实的职业是？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 53728}, {"id": 76289, "content": "木工", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193019xds5nIOlCA0ztH1Y", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 567750}, {"id": 76545, "content": "玩具开发者", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602566}, {"id": 75522, "content": "开一家既卖热饮又卖鲜花的小店，有兴致的时候自己做一两样小甜品送给客人分享，书架上放着我喜欢几本小书～", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182553HuJTPtrYpM2gwXbz.jpg", "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 559927}, {"id": 75778, "content